---
title: Moroccan-Spiced Chicken Thighs with Freekeh, Butternut Squash and Lemon Crema
description: Such a medley of exciting and fresh flavours, this dish had a lot going for it. Tender grains, lots of veggies, fresh spices and a tangy kick of lemon crema make this chicken recipe one you'll want to make again and again!
